            <div class="text-center mb-10">
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gold">Financial Modeling</span>
                <h2 class="text-5xl mt-2 mb-2">Valuation Terminal</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-light">Calculate the Cost of Attrition vs. Retention Investment.</p>
